    Venus dumped Quasar into the Strong Cell, so she wouldnt be effected by 
the Energon Radiation that filled the ship like oxygen. Safe and secure, 
Venus disarmed the girl from all her visable weapons.
    Ominous came to look at the bot. She seemed to be a Predacon....but she 
would have to be converted to serve them. It might be a messy procedure. 
"We'll begin when that blast she took heals. In the meantime, I want 
Odiphious to monitor her. Akron will go and see where they're taking 
Darkmouse, and from there we shall attack."
    "Yes sir. I will prep the surgery room. Venus, set up the Liquid Energon 
transfer tube. And keep an emergency CR chamber on hand, just in case." 
Subcommander Putnam ordered as Ominous walked away to the bridge.

    Akron skidded out from the base, headed in the direction of Darkmouses 
base. If she was there, she could follow them, if not score the litte vermine 
for herself.
